<P>
I wanted to congratulate the Los Angeles Times for this great idea of Nuestro 
Tiempo. My mother likes to read the section in Spanish. I like to read it in 
English, and sometimes glance at the articles in Spanish, too. 
</P>
<P>
RAQUEL GARCIA 
</P>
<P>
Los Angeles 
</P>
