during rare relaxed moment at fire station are firefighters Ray Tong, left, and 
Ron Calkins. ; Photo, Station 12 firefighters battle blaze that engulfs car. It 
was believed the fire was deliberately set. ; Photo, Fire Capt. Ralph Haynes 
puts on armored vest. Gang activity in area covered by Station 12 has made use 
