BORQUEZ, LAWSON SELECT COLLEGES 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Sprinter Tony Borquez of Alemany High and distance runner Craig Lawson of 
Granada Hills High will attend USC and Brigham Young, respectively, in the 
fall. 
