week. But Bush did not see Deukmejian, although he was accompanied by 
Republican members of Congress. Bush gave speeches on high technology in Palo 
Alto, visited a ranch seized from drug traffickers in Orange County, spoke 
briefly to Latinos, attended a baseball game and met with former President 
Ronald Reagan. 
</P>
